short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A browser extension to summarize open tabs into Obsidian markdown files.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: tabSidian saves your open tabs to a markdown document. You can customize the markdown and select which tabs to save. Markdown document can be used in Obsidian, Notion or other apps to organize your browsing data.
